commit.message: Add tests for duplicate methods on traits/impls.

files.patch:
@@ -0,0 +1,17 @@

+
+struct Foo;
+impl Foo {
+    fn orange(&self){}
+    fn orange(&self){}   //~ ERROR error: duplicate definition of method `orange`
+}
+
+fn main() {}
